will never improve then.

371
00:19:54,630 --> 00:19:55,760
Still, an individual

372
00:19:56,480 --> 00:19:57,390
has limits.

373
00:20:00,590 --> 00:20:01,320
That's right.

374
00:20:03,560 --> 00:20:04,630
If you want to make a change,

375
00:20:05,870 --> 00:20:07,350
you can't rely on the individual.

376
00:20:08,390 --> 00:20:10,000
It relies on the policy.

377
00:20:13,720 --> 00:20:14,560
Su Li,

378
00:20:16,910 --> 00:20:18,150
