379
00:20:19,000 --> 00:20:20,000
You want to create

380
00:20:20,110 --> 00:20:22,670
a better Haicheng Hospital.

381
00:20:24,390 --> 00:20:25,040
However,

382
00:20:25,590 --> 00:20:27,390
have you considered this?

383
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:36,480
Look.

384
00:20:36,760 --> 00:20:38,830
You've imitated the revenue model

385
00:20:38,830 --> 00:20:41,830
and operating model of Man'ou Clinic,

386
00:20:42,670 --> 00:20:44,320
but you have neglected

387
00:20:44,830 --> 00:20:49,110
its core concept used
to manage hospitals.

388
00:20:51,350 --> 00:20:53,320
What is the core concept?

389
00:21:02,280 --> 00:21:04,280
Patients first.

390
00:21:12,430 --> 00:21:13,870
Patients first.

391
00:21:15,350 --> 00:21:17,040
A united team.

392
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:20,080
These three lines,

393
00:21:20,910 --> 00:21:22,110
us three doctors,

394
00:21:23,520 --> 00:21:25,430
and three different concepts.

395
00:21:27,960 --> 00:21:29,630
Work in solidarity

396
00:21:30,910 --> 00:21:32,830
and march forward together.

397
00:21:48,830 --> 00:21:49,590
Yes.

398
00:21:52,560 --> 00:21:53,830
Our generation

399
00:21:53,960 --> 00:21:54,910
of Haicheng Hospital

400
00:21:56,190 --> 00:21:58,000
