403
00:22:03,150 --> 00:22:05,280
You need to be united.

404
00:22:15,150 --> 00:22:18,350
It's only Haicheng when you're united.

405
00:22:20,430 --> 00:22:22,150
That is the future.

406
00:22:29,760 --> 00:22:30,430
Lin,

407
00:22:31,910 --> 00:22:32,910
I watched you grow

408
00:22:33,080 --> 00:22:34,480
in our hospital.

409
00:22:35,390 --> 00:22:36,870
You were so young back then,

410
00:22:37,000 --> 00:22:38,040
so handsome.

411
00:22:40,150 --> 00:22:41,150
Right now,

412
00:22:42,480 --> 00:22:43,760
your hair is gray.

413
00:22:48,390 --> 00:22:51,520
I recommended you as vice president.

414
00:22:54,830 --> 00:22:56,960
I'm not here to blame

415
00:22:57,040 --> 00:22:57,870
or criticize you.

416
00:22:58,480 --> 00:23:00,430
I just want to remind you

417
00:23:02,910 --> 00:23:03,910
that all these years,

418
00:23:04,670 --> 00:23:06,830
you've been the doctor

419
00:23:07,630 --> 00:23:09,080
