425
00:23:21,630 --> 00:23:22,910
Are they rich people?

426
00:23:24,830 --> 00:23:25,480
No.

427
00:23:26,670 --> 00:23:28,350
They are people who come to us

428
00:23:28,480 --> 00:23:29,670
for treatment.

429
00:23:30,390 --> 00:23:32,240
They only come to us

430
00:23:32,590 --> 00:23:34,390
for you, Dr. Lin Ge,

431
00:23:34,520 --> 00:23:36,150
to treat them.

432
00:23:50,760 --> 00:23:52,430
