00:26:13,520 --> 00:26:14,910
My grandparents took me away.

466
00:26:16,560 --> 00:26:17,480
I told myself

467
00:26:17,670 --> 00:26:18,670
I had to find out the truth

468
00:26:19,520 --> 00:26:20,910
and clear my father's name.

469
00:26:22,760 --> 00:26:23,670
At that time, I was already enrolled

470
00:26:23,720 --> 00:26:24,190
in medical school.

471
00:26:27,630 --> 00:26:29,240
My grandmother passed away
five years ago.

472
00:26:31,190 --> 00:26:32,040
I thought it was time

473
00:26:32,040 --> 00:26:33,190
to investigate the incident.

474
00:26:35,040 --> 00:26:36,390
You were assigned to South University,

475
00:26:37,280 --> 00:26:38,110
so I signed up

476
00:26:38,110 --> 00:26:39,240
to study interventional therapy there.

477
00:26:39,960 --> 00:26:40,720
No wonder.

478
00:26:42,520 --> 00:26:44,190
You were doing well in neurosurgery,

479
00:26:45,630 --> 00:26:46,870
but you insisted
on studying interventional therapy.

480
00:26:47,390 --> 00:26:49,040
You kept asking

