494
00:27:14,190 --> 00:27:14,830
Thus,

495
00:27:15,870 --> 00:27:16,720
you're in Haicheng Hospital

496
00:27:17,870 --> 00:27:18,720
to investigate the truth

497
00:27:18,720 --> 00:27:19,800
of what happened.

