00:29:18,110 --> 00:29:18,830
I'll operate on her.

561
00:29:19,790 --> 00:29:20,720
Dr. Chen, hurry!

562
00:29:20,830 --> 00:29:21,390
Dr. Chen.

563
00:29:21,630 --> 00:29:22,630
We have a child.

