00:29:54,630 --> 00:29:55,070
Okay.

581
00:29:55,760 --> 00:29:56,350
Doctor.

582
00:29:56,590 --> 00:29:57,310
Didn't you say you're going

583
00:29:57,480 --> 00:29:58,240
to operate on my mom?

584
00:29:58,520 --> 00:29:59,920
Your mom isn't in danger now.

585
00:30:00,200 --> 00:30:01,110
If we don't save the girl now,
